---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<div class="pitch-card lg:flex p-4 py-8 rounded-xl flex-grow shadow-xl">
  <!-- Title + what we do -->
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center lg:w-3/5 gap-4 px-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl">What we do:</h2>
    <span
      >Triple Crown Digital aims to support businesses expanding the universe of
      crypto marketplaces by helping with their go-to-market, liquidity and
      messaging strategies. By leveraging decades of team experience in the
      digital asset industry as well as skill sets honed at traditional finance
      firms and crypto startups, we work closely with leadership teams to reach
      their milestones and achieve goals. 
      <br />
      <br />
      Send us an email if you’d like to chat and see how we could be useful.
    </span>
  </div>

  <!-- Logo -->
  <div class="flex md:flex-grow justify-center items-center">
    <img
      class="rounded-xl h-60 w-60 sm:mx-auto lg:m-0"
      src="/site-imgs/logo.jpeg"
      alt="Triple Crown Digital Logo"
    />
  </div>
</div>
